query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('serverfault')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-ec2',
'amazon-web-services',
'iptables',
'powershell',
'raid',
'ssl',
'ubuntu',
'vpn',
'windows',
'windows-server-2008',
'windows-server-2008-r2');
